{"type":"assistant","message":{"type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I also need to handle the `awaiting_open` actions in the `ProjectDetail` context. Looking at the `awaiting_open` handler, it uses `app.selected_issue()` and `app.selected_issue_url()`. When in ProjectDetail (not Detail), `selected_issue()` returns from filtered_issues (MyIssues), not from project issues. Let me also add `selected_project_issue_url()`:"},{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_vrtx_012P3AxycRtWh6guQ8q65JkG","name":"Read","input":{"path":"/Users/jmawson/Development/sourcery/ishi/src/app.rs","read_range":[414,420]}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1062,"cache_read_input_tokens":95879,"output_tokens":194,"max_tokens":168000,"service_tier":"standard"}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"T-019cff84-fd1e-7738-a45c-2a0f8dd421b5"}
