{"type":"assistant","message":{"type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Summary — 実装完了 (じっそうかんりょう — implementation complete):**\n\n- Added `DetailOrigin` enum to track whether the Detail view was entered from MyIssues or ProjectDetail\n- Added `select_project_issue()` method — pressing Enter on a project issue now opens the reused Detail view (with description, comments, threads, etc.)\n- Updated `back_to_list()` to return to `ProjectDetail` when the detail was opened from project context, and `MyIssues` when from the my-issues context\n- Added `context_issue()` which returns the correct issue based on current view context, used by `selected_issue()` and `selected_issue_url()`\n- Wired up `Select` and `OpenIn` key actions in the `ProjectDetail` key handler in `main.rs`\n- Added 14 new tests covering: select/back navigation, detail origin tracking, context-aware issue resolution, and URL resolution from project context\n- All 187 tests pass, no new clippy warnings"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":499,"cache_read_input_tokens":115500,"output_tokens":241,"max_tokens":168000,"service_tier":"standard"}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"T-019cff84-fd1e-7738-a45c-2a0f8dd421b5"}
